        "description": "<p>Com este plugin \u00e9 poss\u00edvel adicionar informa\u00e7\u00f5es sobre pre\u00e7o parcelado e\/ou pre\u00e7o para pagamento \u00e0 vista, nas p\u00e1ginas que listam todos os produtos e na p\u00e1gina individual de cada produto.<\/p>\n<p>Possui uma p\u00e1gina de op\u00e7\u00f5es em &#8220;WooCommerce&#8221; &gt; &#8220;Parcelas&#8221; onde \u00e9 poss\u00edvel definir:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Op\u00e7\u00f5es para parcelamento:\n<ul>\n<li>Prefixo;<\/li>\n<li>Quantidade de parcelas;<\/li>\n<li>Sufixo;<\/li>\n<li>Valor m\u00ednimo da parcela.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li>Op\u00e7\u00f5es para pagamento \u00e0 vista:\n<ul>\n<li>Prefixo;<\/li>\n<li>Valor do desconto;<\/li>\n<li>Tipo do desconto (% ou fixo);<\/li>\n<li>Sufixo;<\/li>\n<li>\u00c9 poss\u00edvel desabilitar o pre\u00e7o \u00e0 vista e\/ou o pre\u00e7o parcelado em qualquer produto, individualmente.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li>Posic\u00e3o e alinhamento dessas informa\u00e7\u00f5es dentro das p\u00e1ginas;<\/li>\n<li>Estilizar as informa\u00e7\u00f5es de parcelamento e de pagamento \u00e0 vista, separadamente e por p\u00e1gina.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>As imagens falam por si mesmas: <a href=\"https:\/\/wordpress.org\/plugins\/woocommerce-parcelas\/screenshots\/\" rel=\"ugc\">WooCommerce Parcelas Screenshots<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Compat\u00edvel, tamb\u00e9m, com produto vari\u00e1vel e agrupado.<\/strong><\/p>\n",
        "installation": "<ol>\n<li>Fa\u00e7a o upload do plugin atrav\u00e9s do painel do WordPress, indo em &#8220;Plugins&#8221; &gt; &#8220;Adicionar Novo&#8221;;<\/li>\n<li>Ative o plugin indo at\u00e9 o menu &#8220;Plugins&#8221;;<\/li>\n<li>Habilite a funcionalidade do plugin e defina suas op\u00e7\u00f5es em &#8220;WooCommerce&#8221; &gt; &#8220;Parcelas&#8221;.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n",
        "faq": "\n<dt id='funciona%20com%20o%20ponto%20como%20separador%20decimal%3F'>\nFunciona com o ponto como separador decimal?\n<\/h4>\n<p>\n<p>Sim.<\/p>\n<\/p>\n<dt id='funciona%20com%20produto%20vari%C3%A1vel%20e%20agrupado%3F'>\nFunciona com produto vari\u00e1vel e agrupado?\n<\/h4>\n<p>\n<p>Sim.<\/p>\n<\/p>\n<dt id='%C3%89%20poss%C3%ADvel%20definir%20um%20pre%C3%A7o%20para%20pagamento%20%C3%A0%20vista%20%28boleto%29%3F'>\n\u00c9 poss\u00edvel definir um pre\u00e7o para pagamento \u00e0 vista (boleto)?\n<\/h4>\n<p>\n<p>Sim.<\/p>\n<\/p>\n<dt id='quero%20adicionar%20juros%2C%20%C3%A9%20poss%C3%ADvel%3F'>\nQuero adicionar juros, \u00e9 poss\u00edvel?\n<\/h4>\n<p>\n<p>Ainda n\u00e3o, talvez, em breve&#8230;<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/filipecsweb.com.br\/contato\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Bugs e Sugest\u00f5es<\/a><\/p>\n<\/p>\n\n",
        "changelog": "<h4>1.3.5<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Corrige estilo: cores etc nao estavam sendo aplicadas.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.3.4<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Adiciona versao na query string dos arquivos js, carregados no produto variavel, para evitar cache.<\/li>\n<li>Cria opcao &#8220;Habilitar nos produtos fora de estoque?&#8221;.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.3.3<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Corrige erro javascript quando o produto variavel possuia pre\u00e7os iguais.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.3.2<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Implementa\u00e7\u00e3o de possibilidade de sobrescrita de quantidade de parcelas e pre\u00e7o \u00e0 vista por produto.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.2.9<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Declara\u00e7\u00e3o &#8220;!important&#8221; foi adicionada aos valores das propriedades em CSS;<\/li>\n<li>A fun\u00e7\u00e3o depreciada get_product() foi substitu\u00edda por wc_get_product();<\/li>\n<li>O dom\u00ednio de texto &#8216;woocommerce-parcelas&#8217; foi alterado para &#8216;wc-parcelas&#8217;.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.2.8<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Corrigido bug que impedia o pre\u00e7o \u00e0 vista de ser mostrado, em produtos vari\u00e1veis com pre\u00e7os diferentes, caso o parcelamento estivesse desativado.<\/li>\n<li>Adicionada op\u00e7\u00e3o para desabilitar o pre\u00e7o parcelado em produtos espec\u00edficos.<\/li>\n<li>Adicionada op\u00e7\u00e3o para mudar a posi\u00e7\u00e3o de alinhamento (centralizar) das informa\u00e7\u00f5es.<\/li>\n<li>Adicionada sess\u00e3o com op\u00e7\u00f5es que possibilitam a estiliza\u00e7\u00e3o\/formata\u00e7\u00e3o das informa\u00e7\u00f5es.<\/li>\n<li>Corrigida URL do bot\u00e3o &#8216;Bugs e Sugest\u00f5es&#8217;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.2.7<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Adicionada op\u00e7\u00e3o para desabilitar o pre\u00e7o \u00e0 vista em produtos espec\u00edficos.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.2.6<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Corrigido compatibilidade com produto agrupado. Adicionada op\u00e7\u00e3o para definir a posi\u00e7\u00e3o do pre\u00e7o parcelado e \u00e0 vista. Adicionada op\u00e7\u00e3o para definir um valor de desconto para pagamentos \u00e0 vista.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.2.5.3<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Settings link below plugin name was fixed.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.2.5.1<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Minimum value, with comma, wasn&#8217;t working in variable product.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.2.5<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Some improvements habe been mave in code.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.2.4<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Some bugs were fixed. Some actions were added. One filter was added. Better css classes were added.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.2.3<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>js code was fixed to work correctly when decimal separator is point.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.2.2<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fully compatible with variable product.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.2.1<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Translated to english.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.2<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Installment minimum value field added.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.1<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Prefix and suffix fields added.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Plugin release.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n",
        "screenshots": "<ol><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/woocommerce-parcelas\/assets\/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=2980933\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/woocommerce-parcelas\/assets\/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=2980933\" alt=\"Tela de configura\u00e7\u00e3o (Geral)\"><\/a><p>Tela de configura\u00e7\u00e3o (Geral)<\/p><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/woocommerce-parcelas\/assets\/screenshot-2.jpg?rev=2980933\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/woocommerce-parcelas\/assets\/screenshot-2.jpg?rev=2980933\" alt=\"Tela de configura\u00e7\u00e3o (Posi\u00e7\u00e3o)\"><\/a><p>Tela de configura\u00e7\u00e3o (Posi\u00e7\u00e3o)<\/p><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/woocommerce-parcelas\/assets\/screenshot-3.jpg?rev=2980933\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/woocommerce-parcelas\/assets\/screenshot-3.jpg?rev=2980933\" alt=\"P\u00e1ginas que listam os produtos (frontend)\"><\/a><p>P\u00e1ginas que listam os produtos (frontend)<\/p><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/woocommerce-parcelas\/assets\/screenshot-4.jpg?rev=2980933\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/woocommerce-parcelas\/assets\/screenshot-4.jpg?rev=2980933\" alt=\"P\u00e1gina indivudual do produto (frontend)\"><\/a><p>P\u00e1gina indivudual do produto (frontend)<\/p><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/woocommerce-parcelas\/assets\/screenshot-5.jpg?rev=2980933\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/woocommerce-parcelas\/assets\/screenshot-5.jpg?rev=2980933\" alt=\"P\u00e1gina indivudual do produto (backend)\"><\/a><p>P\u00e1gina indivudual do produto (backend)<\/p><\/li><\/ol>",
        "reviews": "<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Plugin causou erro no site<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"4 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"4\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/taticlima\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/67e5866e1f26ed5acdc7869d716725eb?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/67e5866e1f26ed5acdc7869d716725eb?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/taticlima\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">taticlima<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 26, 2020<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">Ap\u00f3s atualiza\u00e7\u00e3o para as novas vers\u00f5es do wordpress e woocommerce, o plugin passou a apresentar erro nas p\u00e1ginas onde ele est\u00e1 aparente. Infelizmente n\u00e3o ser\u00e1 poss\u00edvel utiliz\u00e1-lo mais at\u00e9 que o erro seja reparado e volte a ser compat\u00edvel com as vers\u00f5es mais recentes. Uma pena.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Muito bom<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/ricardods\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/feb04624c3e963745d324d6fc9717f8c?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/feb04624c3e963745d324d6fc9717f8c?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/ricardods\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Ricardo <small>(ricardods)<\/small><\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">July 4, 2017<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">Leve, funciona bem, faz o que precisa!\n\nObrigado<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Atualiza\u00e7\u00e3o Plugin<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/ranaves\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/02d0b0b855d4bde8605f59f0d29329f4?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/02d0b0b855d4bde8605f59f0d29329f4?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/ranaves\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">ranaves<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 24, 2017<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">Filipe,\n\n   Tem previs\u00e3o quando poder\u00e1 disponibilizar uma nova atualiza\u00e7\u00e3o do plugin? A info. que aparece \u00e9 de 1 ano atr\u00e1s.\n\nRaphael<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Excelente!<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/johnnydemarch\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/46a3c18e65b20c3e6a648a752d3ebf7e?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/46a3c18e65b20c3e6a648a752d3ebf7e?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/johnnydemarch\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Johnny Demarch <small>(johnnydemarch)<\/small><\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 21, 2016<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">Mt bom!<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Shortcode<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/tilitoral\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/991ef4267cce6f595611669581a2635f?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/991ef4267cce6f595611669581a2635f?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/tilitoral\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">tilitoral<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">September 14, 2016<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">O plugin \u00e9 excelente!! Gostaria de saber se ele possui algum shortcode para poder exibir ele em um local personalizado. Estou personalizando a pagina de produto e estou com esta dificuldade.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Ajustar fun\u00e7\u00e3o<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/hudsonalves\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/d2f3306b89a80aea7c26e3c36a9862d2?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/d2f3306b89a80aea7c26e3c36a9862d2?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/hudsonalves\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">hudsonalves<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">September 3, 2016<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><p>Prezados como v\u00e3o? Espero que bem.<\/p>\n<p> O plugin de voc\u00eas \u00e9 bem legal, funciona perfeitamente com o tema que uso, mas tem um por\u00e9m: Utilizo o plugin \"woo sale revolution flashsale\" e quando insiro desconto din\u00e2mico para os produtos o parcelamento de voc\u00eas s\u00f3 reconhece o valor original dando a impress\u00e3o que o plugin de voc\u00eas esta com problema.<\/p>\n<p> Mas quando aplico desconto pelo pr\u00f3prio cadastro do produto ai sim seu pligin reconhece o desconto e parcela corretamente.<\/p>\n<p> Bem, considerem adaptar o plugin para funcionar e reconhecer tamb\u00e9m com o \"woo sale revolution flashsale\" ou qualquer outro plugin de desconto massivo afinal de contas n\u00e3o da para aplicar desconto em todos os produtos um por um usando apenas o woocommerce, \u00e9 necess\u00e1rio um plugin como o \"woo sale revolution flashsale\" que ajude de forma dinamica.\n<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Perfeito<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/brendaferreirap\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/d7068858466a6c21f47773464f22ede7?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/d7068858466a6c21f47773464f22ede7?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/brendaferreirap\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">brendaferreirap<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">September 3, 2016<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><p>\u00d3timo plugin, o melhor que encontrei at\u00e9 agora, f\u00e1cil customiza\u00e7\u00e3o, se ad\u00e9qua perfeitamente na maioria dos temas. A cada atualiza\u00e7\u00e3o fica melhor. Muito obrigada pela contribui\u00e7\u00e3o do plugin. Em breve esterei fazendo doa\u00e7\u00e3o pra contribuir com o projeto.\n<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Excelente plugin!!!<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/danrosa\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/884a01b489c87dd334bc2a9fd3d34650?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/884a01b489c87dd334bc2a9fd3d34650?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/danrosa\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">danrosa<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">September 3, 2016<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><p>Esse plugin \u00e9 muito bom! Cria um chamariz incr\u00edvel da exibi\u00e7\u00e3o de descontos sobre produtos adquiridos \u00e0 vista.  O cliente fica ciente e sabe dos descontos sobre a compra \u00e0 vista sem precisar ficar acessando a p\u00e1gina individual do produto para conferir. Muito bom!!!\n<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n"
    },
    "short_description": "Com este plugin \u00e9 poss\u00edvel adicionar informa\u00e7\u00f5es sobre pre\u00e7o parcelado e\/ou pre\u00e7o para pagamento \u00e0 vista, nas p\u00e1ginas que listam todos os produtos e n &hellip;",
    "description": "<p>Com este plugin \u00e9 poss\u00edvel adicionar informa\u00e7\u00f5es sobre pre\u00e7o parcelado e\/ou pre\u00e7o para pagamento \u00e0 vista, nas p\u00e1ginas que listam todos os produtos e na p\u00e1gina individual de cada produto.<\/p>\n<p>Possui uma p\u00e1gina de op\u00e7\u00f5es em &#8220;WooCommerce&#8221; &gt; &#8220;Parcelas&#8221; onde \u00e9 poss\u00edvel definir:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Op\u00e7\u00f5es para parcelamento:\n<ul>\n<li>Prefixo;<\/li>\n<li>Quantidade de parcelas;<\/li>\n<li>Sufixo;<\/li>\n<li>Valor m\u00ednimo da parcela.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li>Op\u00e7\u00f5es para pagamento \u00e0 vista:\n<ul>\n<li>Prefixo;<\/li>\n<li>Valor do desconto;<\/li>\n<li>Tipo do desconto (% ou fixo);<\/li>\n<li>Sufixo;<\/li>\n<li>\u00c9 poss\u00edvel desabilitar o pre\u00e7o \u00e0 vista e\/ou o pre\u00e7o parcelado em qualquer produto, individualmente.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li>Posic\u00e3o e alinhamento dessas informa\u00e7\u00f5es dentro das p\u00e1ginas;<\/li>\n<li>Estilizar as informa\u00e7\u00f5es de parcelamento e de pagamento \u00e0 vista, separadamente e por p\u00e1gina.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>As imagens falam por si mesmas: <a href=\"https:\/\/wordpress.org\/plugins\/woocommerce-parcelas\/screenshots\/\" rel=\"ugc\">WooCommerce Parcelas Screenshots<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Compat\u00edvel, tamb\u00e9m, com produto vari\u00e1vel e agrupado.<\/strong><\/p>\n",
