        "1.2.2": "<ul>\n<li>For those who wants to displays correct installments in variable product, now the plugin is fully compatible with that product type.<\/li>\n<\/ul>",
        "1.2.1": "<ul>\n<li>The plugin is now completely translated to en_US.<\/li>\n<\/ul>",
        "1.2": "<ul>\n<li>Now you can define an installment minimum value. PagSeguro, for example, set it to 5.<\/li>\n<\/ul>"
